The '''Lunar Station''' was a political outpost for high-ranking [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] officers orbiting the planet [[Danton VI]]. It was not as well guarded as many other Imperial outposts, as the [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer]] ''[[Magellan]]'' seemed to keep any enemies at bay.

